data.description: Probate Short Sale. Own this almost new move in ready home only 1 years old. Featuring stone veneer accents, 2 car garage, nice and open living room area perfect for entertaining guest. Smart home features. Kitchen has a beautiful island, separate pantry along with lots of cabinet space. Screened in lanai over looking the backyard with plenty of space for a pool. No CDD fees and low HOA. Near the Oakleaf Town Center which offers a lot of major shopping, dining and entertainment. Conveniently located close by Cecil Field and NAS Jax. Schedule your tour today!
